  "title": "Service Engineer / Project Engineer X 2 (Mechanical Engineering)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic $3500 - $4000 + Allowance + Variable Bonus</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working location: West / On-site</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working Days: Monday to Friday</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working hours: 8.30am to 5.30pm</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>TRAINING PROVIDED</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Planning / Assign sub-contractors and manpower for the maintenance work and from project handover</strong></li>\n  <li>Supervising &amp; Managing of Sub-contractor to carry maintenance &amp; servicing works</li>\n  <li><strong>Plan and schedule Preventive Maintenance</strong></li>\n  <li>Perform routine check, system back-ups &amp; restoration, troubleshooting and upgrading / improvement of system to ensure optimal functioning of BMS/DCS/PLC/SCADA System</li>\n  <li><strong>Record servicing &amp; maintenance data and generate service report</strong></li>\n  <li>Provide Technical / Operational guidance, engineering solution to the Maintenance Site Facility Management</li>\n  <li>Others ad hoc duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Degree in Mechanical Engineering or equivalent</li>\n  <li><strong>Knowledge on BMS / PLC / HVAC will be a plus point</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Training provided for those without/lesser experience</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
